Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤单地与都会人潮擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.34,0:00:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤单地在一望无尽草原 与风呼啸而过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人想哭的地方究竟是何处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画上两个圈有点像是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.89,0:00:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是非常痛苦的壁垒 不知为何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涌现突破的勇气与Power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为无意间看到 非常严厉的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温柔的一面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.49,0:01:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浦饭幽助与户愚吕的战斗 在一番死斗后赢得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认输的左京 启动了竞技场的爆破装置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在千钧一发中逃脱的幽助他们 望着爆炸的竞技场
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深刻感受到一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而失去幻海师父的空虚 却无法弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户愚吕的赎罪！最大的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.01,0:02:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.23,0:02:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像连悠闲看海的心情都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.07,0:02:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像打了一整年仗的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.05,0:02:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.85,0:02:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙也平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当这家伙变成婆婆的脸时 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像和灵界联络的电话一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波 再帮我把婆婆叫出来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小波 拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵界就像生与死之间的车站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的人不就是去灵界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去是会去 灵界只是中途一站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勉强和这个世界通信的 最多只到灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是他们无法长期留在灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们都要从那里 到不同的目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻海也已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.16,0:04:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踏上了死亡的旅程啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 幻海婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.87,0:04:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 既然已经结束 再想也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人活着应该向前看 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始要玩个痛快 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 学校怎么样？会被留级喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意打起精神 看的人反而难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阎王大人 我们终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.81,0:05:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一段时间没回来 这道门还真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 是我 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？谁是“我”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.69,0:05:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这里很忙 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们好像被忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是我 小阎王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个屋子也让我很怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.29,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过我不在时 工作交由你们办的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的图章不是早就交给你们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…被阎罗王大人发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.98,0:06:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大王命令我们 把工作留给你回来做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阎王大人 快点盖章吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有一定要先处理的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点把这里清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也给我去做事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.91,0:06:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是自已的躺椅最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阎王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 叫他进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是审判之门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将在这里审判你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得没这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去冥狱界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥…冥狱界？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自已想去冥狱界？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥狱界是地狱中最残酷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续一万年给你所有的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且重复一万次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后等着你的是完全的“虚无”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 你还是要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以格斗家的功绩来考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以判你进入罪比较轻的地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？你还有时间考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定的事 我不想改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.17,0:08:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我也无话可说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带他走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阎王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要我找的东西终于找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阎王您说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户愚吕转生为妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为50年前发生的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约在武术会开始的三个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,户愚吕亲眼看着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所有的弟子被一个妖怪杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下毒手的是溃炼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他是武术会 最具冠军相的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他去通知户愚吕 要以“宾客”的身份出场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着就顺手杀死他所有的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛在宣示自已是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时户愚吕被溃炼打得体无完肤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前户愚吕充满自信 认为自已是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就在那时失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的3个月 他完全失去了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武术大会前一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现在幻海等宾客面前的户愚吕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.78,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中已经像是住着一个魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溃炼在大会决赛时 被户愚吕所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后得到冠军的户愚吕 愿望是转生为妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的行动在理论上充满矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使获得冠军 替弟子们报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法消除自已内心的罪恶感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他无法保护自已的弟子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.22,0:11:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过自负的他 没有察觉到自已的不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他无法原谅那样的自已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是他选择走上苦难的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.13,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是对于 自已无法保护的弟子们赎罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.01,0:11:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是自责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走上了拷问自已的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伪装成追求更强力量的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个笨拙的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.22,0:12:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你现在都是力量的全盛期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我常想 要是时光停止就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当人类真不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.97,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到一个永远不老的肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最大的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了解我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我会选择这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想你应该会选这条路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.03,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要走这条路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.21,0:14:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经补偿了一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以当时的妖怪溃炼的力量 谁都不是他的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年前的武术大会结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是不停地 伤害自已 责怪自已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.58,0:15:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最痛快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打败溃炼 转生成妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的我就可以尽情追求力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溃炼杀死我弟子们之后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才明白什么是真正强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该感谢发生了那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻海 你别再管了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还有工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定会变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稍有差错 就会落得我这样的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就再保护他一段时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了最后的最后一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所说的话 竟然是担心打败自已的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.67,0:16:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样的傻瓜真不简单
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使死了也没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你一直以来的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个…大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武术大会冠军的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么都要达成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为冠军能实现任何愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这个大会才有价值
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概知道 浦饭获胜时的愿望是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.94,0:17:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要好好保存幻海的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.45,0:17:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像所有事 都是受到户愚吕控制一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.59,0:18:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本日3点20分的直达船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从首缢岛出发的旅客 都已经完成手续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各位乘客特别小心 不要太晚上船
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些女人在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们要做很多准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.02,0:18:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们应该没有人需要化浓妆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我姐姐之外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说我什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 我只是说我姐姐随时都很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 雪菜的也交给他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又要我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受欢迎不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙由你带着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武术会的冠军带着那家伙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被别人取笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很可爱喔 小波
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于要离开这个岛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了好多事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都故意不提起婆婆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 来了 船来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯旋归去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.12,0:20:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂 你们太无情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个声音是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要丢下老人家自已回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻海师父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.85,0:20:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便替人家做坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗黑武术会 在浦饭队得到冠军后落幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有人继承了左京邪恶的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人留在那座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的幽助他们丝毫不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 浦饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打完暗黑武术会 能够轻松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来之后你马上又要打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙 怎么看都不像是普通的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.53,0:22:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们以前没遇过的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太妙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  新的序章
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.97,0:22:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新战斗就要揭开序幕罗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破碎的镜中映出你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭泣着哭泣着 描绘着弦月的手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.73,0:22:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼唤着谁  消失的恋情背后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.10,0:22:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好几次好几次敲打着你的窗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:23:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被夜晚的加速度追赶在后 仿佛断了线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.96,0:23:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想抱着你用力紧抱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉着失去平衡的亲吻接近爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.97,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼泪悲哀的谎言 在我心中沉睡